Description:

The C++ library used in the PDF Viewer for annotating PDFs.

Local Modifications:

None

Update Instructions:

* Sources are autorolled by https://autoroll.skia.org/r/ink-chromium
* BUILD.gn is manually maintained
  * In order to avoid adding unused JNI implementations, ask gemini to use
    find_required_jni.py to filter the is_android sources list.
  * Note: It does not take into account methods that R8 determines as
    unreachable. Trimming it based on R8 would be more correct, but may
    also lead to more frequent updates.
